Aiysha Hart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aiysha_Hart 0 Aiysha Hart (born 8 August 1990) is an actress and screenwriter best known for her leading roles as Ariadne in the BBC drama series Atlantis, Mona in independent thriller Honour, and Polaire in upcoming film Colette. She also plays DC Sam Railston in Line of Duty. In September 2017, it was announced that she'd been cast as Miriam in Sky One's adaptation of A Discovery of Witches.
